{
  "video_id": "tg_CwQwYNjc",
  "title": "Living sculptures that stand for history's truths | Sethembile Msezane",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12644.0,
      "end_time": 16564.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like for you to take a moment to imagine this with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17964.0,
      "end_time": 21720.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re a little girl of five years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21889.0,
      "end_time": 23618.0,
      "text": "Sitting in front of a mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23642.0,
      "end_time": 25141.0,
      "text": "you ask yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26215.0,
      "end_time": 27406.0,
      "text": "\"Do I exist?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29740.0,
      "end_time": 31726.0,
      "text": "In this space, there is very little context,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31750.0,
      "end_time": 34314.0,
      "text": "and so you move into a different one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34338.0,
      "end_time": 35912.0,
      "text": "one filled with people."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36944.0,
      "end_time": 40207.0,
      "text": "Surely, now you know you&#39;re not a figment of your own imagination."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 41430.0,
      "end_time": 42574.0,
      "text": "You breathe their air."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 43205.0,
      "end_time": 44635.0,
      "text": "You see them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44659.0,
      "end_time": 46730.0,
      "text": "so they must see you."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47168.0,
      "end_time": 50808.0,
      "text": "And yet, you still can&#39;t help but wonder:"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52300.0,
      "end_time": 56129.0,
      "text": "Do I only exist when people speak to me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57616.0,
      "end_time": 59570.0,
      "text": "Pretty heavy thoughts for a child, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60821.0,
      "end_time": 65328.0,
      "text": "But through various artworks that reflect upon our society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65352.00000000001,
      "end_time": 69503.0,
      "text": "I came to understand how a young black girl can grow up"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69527.0,
      "end_time": 74641.0,
      "text": "feeling as if she&#39;s not seen, and perhaps she doesn&#39;t exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76157.0,
      "end_time": 79926.0,
      "text": "You see, if young people don&#39;t have positive images of themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79950.0,
      "end_time": 83118.0,
      "text": "and all that remains are negative stereotypes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 83142.0,
      "end_time": 84967.0,
      "text": "this affects their self-image."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 86340.0,
      "end_time": 89380.0,
      "text": "But it also affects the way that the rest of society treats them."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 91102.0,
      "end_time": 92338.0,
      "text": "I discovered this"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 92362.0,
      "end_time": 96670.0,
      "text": "having lived in Cape Town for about five years at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 96934.0,
      "end_time": 101884.0,
      "text": "I felt a deep sense of dislocation and invisibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 103142.0,
      "end_time": 105205.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t see myself represented."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 106181.0,
      "end_time": 109360.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t see the women who&#39;ve raised me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 109600.0,
      "end_time": 110922.0,
      "text": "the ones who&#39;ve influenced me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 110946.0,
      "end_time": 113676.0,
      "text": "and the ones that have made South Africa what it is today."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 114709.0,
      "end_time": 116644.0,
      "text": "I decided to do something about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 118945.0,
      "end_time": 121517.0,
      "text": "What do you think when you see this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 123571.0,
      "end_time": 125692.0,
      "text": "If you were a black girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 125716.0,
      "end_time": 127451.0,
      "text": "how would it make you feel?"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 129919.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131537.0,
      "text": "Walking down the street,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 131562.0,
      "end_time": 134476.0,
      "text": "what does the city you live in say to you?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 135446.0,
      "end_time": 136882.0,
      "text": "What symbols are present?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 137370.0,
      "end_time": 138971.0,
      "text": "Which histories are celebrated?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 139879.0,
      "end_time": 141105.0,
      "text": "And on the other hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 141129.0,
      "end_time": 142670.0,
      "text": "which ones are omitted?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 143523.0,
      "end_time": 147573.0,
      "text": "You see, public spaces are hardly ever as neutral as they may seem."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 148272.0,
      "end_time": 154292.0,
      "text": "I discovered this when I made this performance in 2013 on Heritage Day."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 156920.0,
      "end_time": 161227.0,
      "text": "Cape Town is teeming with masculine architecture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 161251.0,
      "end_time": 163310.0,
      "text": "monuments and statues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 163334.0,
      "end_time": 165598.0,
      "text": "such as Louis Botha in that photograph."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 166656.0,
      "end_time": 172572.0,
      "text": "This overt presence of white colonial and Afrikaner nationalist men"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 172596.0,
      "end_time": 178180.0,
      "text": "not only echoes a social, gender and racial divide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 178747.0,
      "end_time": 183373.0,
      "text": "but it also continues to affect the way that women --"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 183397.0,
      "end_time": 186596.0,
      "text": "and the way, particularly, black women --"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 186621.0,
      "end_time": 192320.0,
      "text": "see themselves in relation to dominant male figures"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 192560.0,
      "end_time": 193481.0,
      "text": "in public spaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 196896.0,
      "end_time": 199188.0,
      "text": "For this reason, among others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 199212.0,
      "end_time": 201284.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t believe that we need statues."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 202326.0,
      "end_time": 206212.0,
      "text": "The preservation of history and the act of remembering"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 206236.0,
      "end_time": 210571.0,
      "text": "can be achieved in more memorable and effective ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 212244.0,
      "end_time": 216103.0,
      "text": "As part of a year-long public holiday series,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 216127.0,
      "end_time": 220254.0,
      "text": "I use performance art as a form of social commentary"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 220278.0,
      "end_time": 223476.0,
      "text": "to draw people&#39;s attention to certain issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 223500.0,
      "end_time": 229450.0,
      "text": "as well as addressing the absence of the black female body"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 229474.0,
      "end_time": 231712.0,
      "text": "in memorialized public spaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 231736.0,
      "end_time": 233702.0,
      "text": "especially on public holidays."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 234975.0,
      "end_time": 236594.0,
      "text": "Women&#39;s Day was coming up."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 237890.0,
      "end_time": 238802.0,
      "text": "I looked at what the day means --"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 239780.0,
      "end_time": 244435.0,
      "text": "the Women&#39;s March to the union buildings in 1956,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 244459.0,
      "end_time": 246919.0,
      "text": "petitioning against the pass laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 247890.0,
      "end_time": 252696.0,
      "text": "Juxtaposed with the hypocrisy of how women are treated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 252720.0,
      "end_time": 254851.0,
      "text": "especially in public spaces today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 255800.0,
      "end_time": 258380.0,
      "text": "I decided to do something about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 259156.0,
      "end_time": 260813.0,
      "text": "Headline:"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 260837.0,
      "end_time": 266378.0,
      "text": "[Women in miniskirt attacked at taxi rank]"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 268829.0,
      "end_time": 272431.0,
      "text": "How do I comment on such polar opposites?"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 273557.0,
      "end_time": 275698.0,
      "text": "In the guise of my great-grandmother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 275722.0,
      "end_time": 277424.0,
      "text": "I performed bare-breasted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 277449.0,
      "end_time": 280405.0,
      "text": "close to the taxi rank in KwaLanga."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 281146.0,
      "end_time": 283727.0,
      "text": "This space is also called Freedom Square,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 283751.0,
      "end_time": 287604.0,
      "text": "where women were a part of demonstrations against apartheid laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 288976.0,
      "end_time": 295117.0,
      "text": "I was not comfortable with women being seen as only victims in society."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 296359.0,
      "end_time": 298981.0,
      "text": "You might wonder how people reacted to this."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 299751.0,
      "end_time": 302448.0,
      "text": "(Video) Woman: (Cheering)"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 303186.0,
      "end_time": 304774.0,
      "text": "Woman 2 (offscreen): Yes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 312874.0,
      "end_time": 315290.0,
      "text": "Sethembile Msezane: Pretty cool, huh?"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 315954.0,
      "end_time": 318504.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 319702.0,
      "end_time": 322656.0,
      "text": "So I realized that through my performances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 322680.0,
      "end_time": 327764.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been able to make regular people reflect upon their society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 327788.0,
      "end_time": 331488.0,
      "text": "looking at the past as well as the current democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 331512.0,
      "end_time": 334469.0,
      "text": "(Video) Man (offscreen): She&#39;s been there since three o&#39;clock."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 334493.0,
      "end_time": 337227.0,
      "text": "Man 2 (offscreen): Just before three. About an hour still?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 337251.0,
      "end_time": 339215.0,
      "text": "Man 1: Yeah. It&#39;s just a really hot day."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 345531.0,
      "end_time": 347515.0,
      "text": "Man 1: It&#39;s very interesting."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 347539.0,
      "end_time": 349440.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 350144.0,
      "end_time": 351603.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 354463.0,
      "end_time": 359788.0,
      "text": "I think a lot of people are quick to join a group"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 359812.0,
      "end_time": 361684.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s a movement towards something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 361708.0,
      "end_time": 366935.0,
      "text": "but not many people are ready to do something as an individual."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 366959.0,
      "end_time": 369566.0,
      "text": "Man 2: So it&#39;s the individual versus the collective."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 369590.0,
      "end_time": 370746.0,
      "text": "Man 1: Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 370770.0,
      "end_time": 376270.0,
      "text": "So I think her pushing her own individual message in performance ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 377740.0,
      "end_time": 379200.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s powerful."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 380500.0,
      "end_time": 383179.0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think it&#39;s quite powerful that she&#39;s doing it on her own."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 385286.0,
      "end_time": 389427.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d be interested to know why she&#39;s using hair extensions as wings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 389451.0,
      "end_time": 393199.0,
      "text": "or whatever those things are meant to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 394694.0,
      "end_time": 396385.0,
      "text": "They are wings, yes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 398574.0,
      "end_time": 400840.0,
      "text": "Woman 3: With her standing there right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 400864.0,
      "end_time": 404823.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s just my interpretation"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 404848.0,
      "end_time": 408219.0,
      "text": "that we are bringing the statue down"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 408243.0,
      "end_time": 410468.0,
      "text": "and bringing up something"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 410492.0,
      "end_time": 415970.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s supposed to represent African pride, I think."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 415121.0,
      "end_time": 416640.0,
      "text": "Or something like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 417621.0,
      "end_time": 421970.0,
      "text": "Something should stand while Rhodes falls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 421121.0,
      "end_time": 423828.0,
      "text": "I think that&#39;s what it&#39;s saying. Yeah."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 424568.0,
      "end_time": 425784.0,
      "text": "Yes. Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 425808.0,
      "end_time": 429271.0,
      "text": "Man 3: What is behind me represents the African culture."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 429295.0,
      "end_time": 431684.0,
      "text": "We can&#39;t have the colonialist law,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 431708.0,
      "end_time": 434599.0,
      "text": "so we need to remove all these colonial statues."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 434623.0,
      "end_time": 437117.0,
      "text": "We have have our own statues now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 437141.0,
      "end_time": 442130.0,
      "text": "our African leaders -- Bhambatha, Moshoeshoe, Kwame Nkrumah --"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 442370.0,
      "end_time": 446270.0,
      "text": "all those who paid their lives for our liberation."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 446294.0,
      "end_time": 448602.0,
      "text": "We can&#39;t continue in the 21st century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 448626.0,
      "end_time": 450662.0,
      "text": "and after 21 years of democracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 450687.0,
      "end_time": 452827.0,
      "text": "have the colonizers in our own country."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 452851.0,
      "end_time": 455824.0,
      "text": "They belong somewhere. Maybe in a museum; not here."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 455848.0,
      "end_time": 458998.0,
      "text": "I mean learning institutions, places where young people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 459220.0,
      "end_time": 460599.0,
      "text": "young minds are being shaped."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 460624.0,
      "end_time": 465314.0,
      "text": "So we cannot continue to have Louis Botha, Rhodes, all these people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 465338.0,
      "end_time": 468103.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re representing the colonialism."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 470519.0,
      "end_time": 474541.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 475835.0,
      "end_time": 478858.0,
      "text": "Sethembile Msezane: On April 9, 2015,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 478882.0,
      "end_time": 482859.0,
      "text": "the Cecil John Rhodes statue was scheduled to be removed"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 482883.0,
      "end_time": 487970.0,
      "text": "after a month of debates for and against its removal"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 487122.0,
      "end_time": 488910.0,
      "text": "by various stakeholders."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 490434.0,
      "end_time": 494340.0,
      "text": "This caused a widespread interest in statues in South Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 495310.0,
      "end_time": 500362.0,
      "text": "Opinions varied, but the media focused on problematizing"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 500386.0,
      "end_time": 501967.0,
      "text": "the removal of statues."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 504912.0,
      "end_time": 508746.0,
      "text": "On that -- well, that year, I had just begun my master&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 508771.0,
      "end_time": 510636.0,
      "text": "at the University of Cape Town."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 512650.0,
      "end_time": 515455.0,
      "text": "During the time of the debate of the statue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 515479.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518578.00000000006,
      "text": "I had been having reoccurring dreams"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 519413.0,
      "end_time": 520745.0,
      "text": "about a bird."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 521317.0,
      "end_time": 523995.0,
      "text": "And so I started conjuring her"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 524190.00000000006,
      "end_time": 527486.0,
      "text": "mentally, spiritually and through dress."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 529872.0,
      "end_time": 531564.0,
      "text": "On that day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 531589.0,
      "end_time": 535225.0,
      "text": "I happened to be having a meeting with my supervisors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 535249.0,
      "end_time": 538854.0,
      "text": "and they told me that the statue was going to fall on that day."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 539925.0,
      "end_time": 542343.0,
      "text": "I told them that I&#39;d explain later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 542368.0,
      "end_time": 544306.0,
      "text": "but we had to postpone the meeting"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 544330.0,
      "end_time": 548808.0,
      "text": "because I was going to perform her as the statue came down."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 549352.0,
      "end_time": 551232.0,
      "text": "Her name was Chapungu."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 551256.0,
      "end_time": 555636.0,
      "text": "She was a soapstone bird that was looted from Great Zimbabwe"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 555660.0,
      "end_time": 557408.0,
      "text": "in the late 1800s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 557432.0,
      "end_time": 561465.0,
      "text": "and is still currently housed in Cecil John Rhodes&#39;s estate"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 561489.0,
      "end_time": 562639.0,
      "text": "in Cape Town."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 563924.0,
      "end_time": 565100.0,
      "text": "On that day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 565124.0,
      "end_time": 569234.0,
      "text": "I embodied her existence using my body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 569258.0,
      "end_time": 573119.0,
      "text": "while standing in the blazing sun for nearly four hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 575660.0,
      "end_time": 576910.0,
      "text": "As the time came,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 576934.0,
      "end_time": 578477.0,
      "text": "the crane came alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 579210.0,
      "end_time": 580798.0,
      "text": "The people did, too --"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 580822.0,
      "end_time": 581981.0,
      "text": "shouting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 582500.0,
      "end_time": 583242.0,
      "text": "screaming,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 583266.0,
      "end_time": 585175.0,
      "text": "clenching their fists"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 585200.0,
      "end_time": 589820.0,
      "text": "and taking pictures of the moment on their phones and cameras."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 589759.0,
      "end_time": 591278.0,
      "text": "Chapungu&#39;s wings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 591302.0,
      "end_time": 592701.0,
      "text": "along with the crane,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 592725.0,
      "end_time": 597698.0,
      "text": "rose to declare the fall of Cecil John Rhodes."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 598963.0,
      "end_time": 603390.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 604120.0,
      "end_time": 608604.0,
      "text": "Euphoria filled the air as he became absent from his base,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 608629.0,
      "end_time": 610677.0,
      "text": "while she remained still,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 612110.0,
      "end_time": 613610.0,
      "text": "very present,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 613634.0,
      "end_time": 616279.0,
      "text": "half an hour after his removal."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 618270.0,
      "end_time": 621300.0,
      "text": "Twenty-three years after apartheid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 621540.0,
      "end_time": 624457.0,
      "text": "a new generation of radicals has arisen in South Africa."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 624481.0,
      "end_time": 629354.0,
      "text": "The story of Chapungu and Rhodes in the same space and time"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 629378.0,
      "end_time": 631133.0,
      "text": "asks important questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 631157.0,
      "end_time": 633432.0,
      "text": "related to gender,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 634560.0,
      "end_time": 635333.0,
      "text": "power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 635357.0,
      "end_time": 637137.0,
      "text": "self-representation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 637162.0,
      "end_time": 638751.0,
      "text": "history making"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 638775.0,
      "end_time": 640203.0,
      "text": "and repatriation."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 643700.0,
      "end_time": 644220.0,
      "text": "From then on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 644244.0,
      "end_time": 649465.0,
      "text": "I realized that my spiritual beliefs and dreams"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 649489.0,
      "end_time": 652400.0,
      "text": "texture my material reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 653249.0,
      "end_time": 656612.0,
      "text": "But for me, Chapungu&#39;s story felt incomplete."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 656636.0,
      "end_time": 658385.0,
      "text": "This soapstone bird,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 658409.0,
      "end_time": 662776.0,
      "text": "a spiritual medium and messenger of God and the ancestors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 662800.0,
      "end_time": 664899.0,
      "text": "needed me to continue her story."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 665501.0,
      "end_time": 669917.0,
      "text": "And so I dabbled in the dream space a little bit more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 669941.0,
      "end_time": 672572.0,
      "text": "and this is how \"Falling\" was born."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 679209.0,
      "end_time": 680675.0,
      "text": "[A film by Sethembile Msezane]"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 680700.0,
      "end_time": 683945.0,
      "text": "(Video) (A capella singing)"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 711809.0,
      "end_time": 715000.0,
      "text": "[FALLING]"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 718734.0,
      "end_time": 721712.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 722571.0,
      "end_time": 723721.0,
      "text": "In the film,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 723745.0,
      "end_time": 727503.0,
      "text": "Zimbabwe, South Africa and Germany share a common story"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 727527.0,
      "end_time": 731217.0,
      "text": "about the soapstone birds that were looted from Great Zimbabwe."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 732156.0,
      "end_time": 734468.0,
      "text": "After Zimbabwe gained its independence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 734493.0,
      "end_time": 738414.0,
      "text": "all the birds except for one were returned to the monument."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 738984.0,
      "end_time": 744110.0,
      "text": "\"Falling\" explores the mythological belief that there will be unrest"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 744134.0,
      "end_time": 746811.0,
      "text": "until the final bird is returned."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 748718.0,
      "end_time": 750400.0,
      "text": "Through my work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 750650.0,
      "end_time": 753495.0,
      "text": "I have realized a lot about the world around me:"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 754570.0,
      "end_time": 756530.0,
      "text": "how we move through spaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 757109.0,
      "end_time": 759444.0,
      "text": "who we choose to celebrate"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 759468.0,
      "end_time": 761123.0,
      "text": "and who we remember."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 761900.0,
      "end_time": 765889.0,
      "text": "Now I look in the mirror and not only see an image of myself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 766679.0,
      "end_time": 769754.0,
      "text": "but of the women who have made me who I am today."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 770536.0,
      "end_time": 773584.0,
      "text": "I stand tall in my work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 773608.0,
      "end_time": 776690.0,
      "text": "celebrating women&#39;s histories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 776930.0,
      "end_time": 778621.0,
      "text": "in the hope that perhaps one day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 779314.0,
      "end_time": 782569.0,
      "text": "no little black girl has to ever feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 782594.0,
      "end_time": 784480.0,
      "text": "like she doesn&#39;t exist."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 784504.0,
      "end_time": 785724.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 785748.0,
      "end_time": 789993.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}